com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.data

Class WZDataItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.data.WZDataItem

  • public class WZDataItem
extends Object
    The primary class for representing stream metadata, the server connection query string, and WZDataEvent parameters
    See Also:
    WZStreamConfig.setStreamMetadata(WZDataMap), WZStreamConfig.setConnectionParameters(WZDataMap), com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.broadcast.WZBroadcast#sendDataEvent(WZDataEvent), com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.broadcast.WZBroadcast#registerDataEventListener(String, WZDataEvent.EventListener)
